    "type": "message",
    "text": "This is my favorite paper on the problems of floating point: <https://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/hal-00576641v1/document>. I periodically daydream about replacing them with something like unums: <http://www.johngustafson.net/presentations/Unums2.0slides-withNotes.pdf>",
