    "client_msg_id": "850c517c-df30-4543-b017-e86fa74541aa",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Hello, I’m Jesse.  <@U85MWBKEY> recently invited me to this group. I’m interested in building a company around the idea of replacing programmers with computers to the greatest extent possible. I’ve been using Gist as a sort of blog lately. I’ve posted three weekly articles so far. Check them out to get an idea of the sort of things I’m thinking about:\n<https://gist.github.com/JesseAldridge/3fd430aab1c29c5ac0a74a5ad359092b>\n<https://gist.github.com/JesseAldridge/5d38ea1c6147800c607ad6e727dfd4e8>\n<https://gist.github.com/JesseAldridge/17c1bcd7ecd17ed5ce98fef0132c5c98>",
